ğŸ¯ 3. K-Map Simplification Rules
    âœ… Rule 1: Grouping 1ï¸âƒ£s (for SOP) or 0ï¸âƒ£s (for POS)
    
        The goal is to group 1s (for Sum of Products - SOP) or 0s (for Product of Sums - POS).
        Groups should be in powers of 2: 1, 2, 4, 8, etc. ğŸ”¢
        Larger groups = simpler expression! ğŸ˜
        Groups must be rectangular or square ğŸ“

    âœ… Rule 2: Wrapping is Allowed
    
        Edges wrap around like a torus (donut shape) ğŸ©
        Top row connects to the bottom row
        Leftmost column connects to the rightmost column

    âœ… Rule 3: Writing the Expression

        Each group gives a simplified Boolean term
        Final equation is the sum (OR) of all groups

